{"type": "article", "id": 18358, "title": "Nendo 新接了箱包的活，从 logo 到旗舰店都一并设计了", "description": "要观察如何塑造品牌的一致性，这是一个好案例。", "date": "2015-12-02T07:17:03Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 3000, "name": "店铺设计"}, {"id": 247, "name": "Nendo"}, {"id": 19633, "name": "proteca"}], "category": 17, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 8, "praise_count": 227, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702122039XcGIDldeguQpiyqs.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t日本箱包公司 proteca 成立十周年，在东京开设了第一家旗舰店，请到 nendo 做室内设计，更换了 logo，并顺带设计了一个箱子。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t这家旗舰店在千代田区，三面墙全部做成了木框的样子，像是层层堆积上去的。<span>架子的结构是由两层木板做成的，中间留有空隙，也模拟了木箱的感觉。而</span>地上的展台也是高低错落的木箱，看起来整齐有序，就是旅行箱本身需要发挥的功能。设计的理念也源于此，<span>木箱</span>在运输时用来装货，与旅行箱都有运输货物的功能是一致的。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>木框内侧全部涂白，让箱子在灯光下显得更亮，能注意到表面的纹理。而放箱子的表面被刷成了黑色，能帮助反光。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702122026PpAG6fjdHIviDJBm.jpg\" width=\"820\" height=\"461\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.56219512\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702122027HIQN9oqnVivdT2AK.jpg\" width=\"820\" height=\"547\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66707317\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702122027PQHTLuowVqj3c0Wr.jpg\" width=\"820\" height=\"547\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66707317\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607021220282mTIUhfpEePv8bB7.jpg\" width=\"820\" height=\"547\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66707317\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702122028B4yzxnrRZk1YHVog.jpg\" width=\"820\" height=\"547\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66707317\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702122029ljmM64KRnhbYCw9W.jpg\" width=\"820\" height=\"547\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66707317\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t新的 logo 是从“Proteca”的“P”中幻化出来的，像打了一个小节，有手推箱的感觉。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702122029vg4JrjYa3ucVnqNO.jpg\" width=\"820\" height=\"580\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.70731707\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702122030Y4hKigAEPOGkHmzq.jpg\" width=\"820\" height=\"547\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66707317\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702122030n9emJbDWhZj012ou.jpg\" width=\"820\" height=\"547\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66707317\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\tnendo 曾经设计过一种可爱版的手提箱，这款 proteca 360 更注重功能性。它的外壳使用高分子聚碳酸酯制作，上面有确保硬度的棱纹结，能反射出一定的光线变化。旅行箱最大的特征是四周环绕的拉链，使箱子可以从任意一面打开，很方便。还有放在旅行箱里面的装衣物的小袋和内衣，nendo也一并设计了。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t这款旅行箱共有 6 种颜色和 4 种型号。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702122031IbcxsLuHdFVmUkgf.jpg\" width=\"820\" height=\"580\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.70731707\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702122031t8bYUMgeHFB6qTzs.jpg\" width=\"820\" height=\"547\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66707317\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702122032tLWxdE7TRBw9rHkY.jpg\" width=\"820\" height=\"547\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66707317\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702122032Qno3x0lKDUSH8zye.jpg\" width=\"820\" height=\"547\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66707317\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702122033NOecasELTAqVMY13.jpg\" width=\"820\" height=\"547\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66707317\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607021220330IjaqdLDep4lXVR5.jpg\" width=\"820\" height=\"547\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66707317\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702122034L085G9gYxbWBDP4k.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"546\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/2016070212203438mdwpCDOQt0MiIR.jpg\" width=\"820\" height=\"547\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" style=\"text-align:center;\" data-ratio=\"0.66707317\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702122034EcjaSIm7XHZdbOol.jpg\" width=\"820\" height=\"547\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66707317\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702122035jHwdEb6tTe5oplWG.jpg\" width=\"820\" height=\"547\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66707317\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702122035thDeEW0f6JLupgdw.jpg\" width=\"820\" height=\"547\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66707317\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607021220364C1FujDBJNVYhpne.jpg\" width=\"820\" height=\"547\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66707317\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t除此之外，考虑全面的 nendo 还设计了专门的展示台，也是从木箱的概念出发。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702122037xjHRygmIkeFdsCLp.jpg\" width=\"820\" height=\"580\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.70731707\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702122037Vc7Rtg94IJdabyWB.jpg\" width=\"820\" height=\"547\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66707317\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702122037oNdAVfaSbvWuUlwJ.jpg\" width=\"820\" height=\"547\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66707317\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702122039RmizunpTso8gGQ6N.jpg\" width=\"820\" height=\"547\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66707317\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t图片来自 <a href=\"http://www.nendo.jp/en/works/proteca-2/proteca-shop/?erelease\" target=\"_blank\">nendo</a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\n\n"}